<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:733.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">〔註〕疑問詞作為主語時要帶助詞「が」。第</span><span class="cls_008">１０</span><span class="cls_009">課中學過了詢問動詞「あり</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:754.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">ます」「います」的主語時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">要用「なにが</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_009">ありますか」「だれが</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_009">います</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:774.54px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">か」</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">詢問形容詞句的主語時也同樣使用助詞「</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:330.60px;top:774.54px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">が」。</span></div>
